Now that singer Rihanna is officially single following her split from boyfriend Saudi businessman, Hassan  Jameel, she is said to be mingling with her ex. This comes after she was spotted hanging out with her rapper ex-boyfriend Drake at a charity event in Brooklyn's Barclays Centre, reports Elle Magazine. She also sparked dating speculation when she was spotted hanging out with ASAP Rocky at the same event. Riri and ASAP also posed together at the British Fashion Awards last month and according to TMZ, she also attended his show in Sweden last month. Meanwhile, Rihanna hasn't spoken publicly about her split from her billionaire beau. The pair called it quits after dating quietly for three years.   